Class PyFileExtended

java.lang.Object
  org.python.core.PyObject
      org.python.core.PyFileExtended
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable
public class PyFileExtended
extends org.python.core.PyObject

A python file wrapper around a java stream, reader/writer or file. ** NOTE ** THIS IS A HACK IN ORDER TO GET PyFile to accept a Reader.
